*Selo* je napustilo mnogo mladih ljudi u potrazi za boljim poslovima. (Many young people have left the village in search of better jobs).

*Selu* su posetili putnici izdaleka. (Travelers from far away have visited the village).

Mnogi ljudi u *selu* su siromašni. (Many people in the village are poor).

*Seljani* su odlučili da udruže svoje napore da bi poboljšali život u selu. (The villagers have decided to unite their efforts to improve life in the village).

U *selu* su postojali zanati koje su se prenosili iz generacije u generaciju. (In the village there were crafts that were passed down from generation to generation).